      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>The light linking editor allows you to control which objects are illuminated or not by a specific light in the scene. </p><h2 id=\"LightLinkingEditor-OpeningLightLinkingEditor\">Opening Light Linking Editor</h2><p>You can open the editor by going to the scene properties <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"27\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/scene_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=26&amp;height=27\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637371/scene_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637401\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"scene_properties.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"7b1a43d9-fa5f-49ee-ad93-6012424b2fb5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/scene_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=26&amp;height=27 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/scene_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=26&amp;height=27 1x\"></span>and click Light Linking Editor</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"408\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_open1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=408&amp;height=71\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637371/light_linking_open1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"72\" data-width=\"409\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637404\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_open1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"7d84e70b-d27a-42b0-b9bd-ff14b1c46479\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_open1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=409&amp;height=72 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_open1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=408&amp;height=71 1x\"></span><p>Or by clicking on the Light Linking Editor menu item in the Object Context Menu.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"550\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_open2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689895&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=550&amp;height=393\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637371/light_linking_open2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689895&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"443\" data-width=\"619\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637389\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_open2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"1ddf1269-1af7-4475-89ea-fd97aeba25c3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_open2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689895&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=619&amp;height=443 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_open2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689895&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=550&amp;height=393 1x\"></span><h2 id=\"LightLinkingEditor-AnExample\">An Example</h2><p>Here's a simple example scene where we want to control the lighting. In this scene, the tank girl is selfish and wants all the lighting to herself, leaving the monkey head in the dark. There are three lights in the scene.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_before.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690475&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=540\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637371/light_linking_before.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690475&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"540\" data-width=\"960\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637413\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_before.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"9f938ba5-42d2-4ef7-b5c0-97236cce4d64\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_before.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690475&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=540 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_before.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690475&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=540 1x\"></span><p>In the editor, we first add a light from the drop down list.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_add_light.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=188\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637371/light_linking_add_light.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"919\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637407\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_add_light.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"410d7d28-e149-4ce5-b4c1-3d0fbb153855\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_add_light.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=919&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_add_light.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=188 1x\"></span><p>Next, we select the object to associate with this light. We can either use the dropdown list.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_add_obj1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690475&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=191\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637371/light_linking_add_obj1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690475&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"256\" data-width=\"907\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637416\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_add_obj1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"a72fd176-3efd-44f1-8de5-e862f93ff5be\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_add_obj1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690475&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=907&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_add_obj1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690475&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=191 1x\"></span><p>Or, use the filter icon to do a search.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_add_obj2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690637&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=192\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637371/light_linking_add_obj2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690637&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"259\" data-width=\"915\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637419\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_add_obj2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"bbb0a74d-4236-4119-bf7b-ce287b571bdb\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_add_obj2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690637&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=915&amp;height=259 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_add_obj2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690637&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=192 1x\"></span><p>Finally, we select what illumination behavior we want.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_illum.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690638&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=194\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637371/light_linking_illum.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690638&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"261\" data-width=\"912\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637422\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_illum.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"8b5876b4-9e2c-488c-899f-0626be8b1c6b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_illum.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690638&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=912&amp;height=261 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_illum.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690638&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=194 1x\"></span><p>The three options are:</p><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Default: this means to just inherit the behavior</p></li><li><p>On: illumination is on for this object from this light</p></li><li><p>Off: illumination is off for this object from this light</p></li></ol><p>In our case we want the illumination to be off. We repeat these steps for the other two lights in the scene.</p><h3 id=\"LightLinkingEditor-Shortcut\">Shortcut</h3><p>You can also use the right click menu to link/unlink an object from a light, as well as change the illumination options. For the right click menu, the last selected object must be a RenderMan light.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"550\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_right_click.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689895&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=550&amp;height=392\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637371/light_linking_right_click.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689895&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"513\" data-width=\"718\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637386\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_right_click.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"b0f6d8a5-e159-4118-9c8a-feb31e10358d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_right_click.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689895&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=718&amp;height=513 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_right_click.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432689895&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=550&amp;height=392 1x\"></span><h2 id=\"LightLinkingEditor-Result\">Result</h2><p>Here's the result after light linking.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690638&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=540\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637371/light_linking_after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690638&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"540\" data-width=\"960\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637425\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_after.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"490bdf37-a1ed-44ee-8394-78b67f93d141\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690638&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=540 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690638&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=540 1x\"></span><p>As you can see, the monkey head is now in the dark.</p><h2 id=\"LightLinkingEditor-Invert\">Invert</h2><p>You can also invert the light linking behavior, meaning that only lights that are linked to a light will be illuminated. If a light has not been added to the light link list, it will still illuminate all objects in the scene. To turn on the invert behavior, go to the scene properties tab and under Light Linking, turn on Invert Light Linking. Note, in order to use Invert Light Linking, Workflow has to be set to RenderMan.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"light_linking_invert.png\" width=\"412\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_invert.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754594331626&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=412&amp;height=393\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637371/light_linking_invert.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754594331626&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"393\" data-width=\"412\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"547029023\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"light_linking_invert.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"4e34e703-ea77-4b07-abb1-88e34b64b553\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_invert.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754594331626&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=412&amp;height=393 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/light_linking_invert.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754594331626&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=412&amp;height=393 1x\"></span><p /><p>Here's an example render scene:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/invert_light_linking2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690137&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=324\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637371/invert_light_linking2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690137&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"611\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637395\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"invert_light_linking2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637371\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"c8584b11-fe44-4440-b9fe-4ff353a36cf1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/invert_light_linking2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690137&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1360&amp;height=648 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637371/invert_light_linking2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432690137&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=680&amp;height=324 1x\"></span><p>In this case the rect light is only illuminating the cube, because only the cube is linked to light. Also, observe that the illumination options are not present in this mode.</p>"
    }
